t-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">对世界</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">红茶的</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">历史渊源</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">品质滋味以及国际</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">市场</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">走向都有深入了解</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><img src="/uploads/editor/image/2016-11-22/1479807671949421.png" title="1479807671949421.png" alt="blob.png"/>&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">&nbsp;与会参加者</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">听课嘉宾定向邀请</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">从事摄影、设计、传媒、</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">文学、艺术、绘画、</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">音乐、演艺、金融等</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 21px; font-family: 宋体;">不同行业</span></strong><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;">人士</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;">不限年龄性别</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;">为保证现场交流效果</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">6<span style="font-family:宋体">人为限</span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;">以报名先后次序为准</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">&nbsp;<img src="/uploads/editor/image/2016-11-22/1479807722459275.png" title="1479807722459275.png" alt="blob.png"/></span></strong></p><p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">课程背景介绍：</span></strong></p><p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">冬日，午后，咖啡馆</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">中</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">一杯</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">温热的</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">伯爵红茶</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">橙红透明的汤色中荡漾着佛手柑的甜香气韵</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">尽显英伦文化的时尚</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">何种爱恨情仇</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">商场拼杀</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">都在一缕馨香中袅袅而去</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">只剩下完整的自己</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">与心相对</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;"><img src="/uploads/editor/image/2016-11-22/1479808164592672.png" title="1479808164592672.png" alt="blob.png"/></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">这是茶的魅力</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">都市红尘中不可少的挚友</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px">&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">为什么这种</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;">英式红茶</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">的名字叫做伯爵</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">它独特的口感又是怎样形成、并且传承百年的呢</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: Calibri; font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">红茶在传统上是西方知道的唯一的茶</span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;"><img src="/uploads/editor/image/2016-11-22/1479808211484465.png" title="1479808211484465.png" alt="blob.png"/><br/></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">时空穿越</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: Calibri; font-size: 14px;">200<span style="font-family:宋体">年前</span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">传说</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;">是</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">因为一次偶然</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">世界上有了红茶</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">武夷山桐木关自然保护区的深处</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">一种带有独特松烟香气的叫作正山小种的红茶</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">因此成为世界红茶的鼻祖</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">然而，谁会想到</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">大山深处的一杯茶</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">在后来</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">几乎撼动了整个世界</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: Calibri; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family:宋体">从</span>1773<span style="font-family:宋体">年的美国独立战争到</span>1840<span style="font-family:宋体">年的鸦片战争</span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">都与它有着直接的关联</span><br/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px">&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">从正山小种到格雷伯爵</span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">一场穿越时空的对话</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">站在红茶的来处坐品红茶</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: Calibri; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family:宋体">廿四节沏之立冬茶</span>——<span style="font-family:宋体">红茶分享沙龙</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">与您一起细数伯爵由来、</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;">慢</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">品红茶神韵、</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;">自在</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">滋味人生</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/uploads/editor/image/2016-11-22/1479807773591910.png" title="1479807773591910.png" alt="blob.png"/></p><p style="line-height: 16px; text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">课程内容设置：</span></strong></p><p style="line-height: 16px; text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px"><br/></span></strong></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">&nbsp;</span><strong style="text-indent: 32px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">英式下午茶的文化与礼仪</span></strong></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">赏茶器</span> <span style="font-family:宋体">：银制</span> <span style="font-family:宋体">托盘</span> <span style="font-family:宋体">骨瓷茶具</span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span 