&#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, SimSun, 宋体, sans-serif; text-align: center; white-space: normal;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; outline: none; table-layout: fixed; word-break: break-all; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; font-size: 14px;"><img src="http://zhenghun.yicehua.cn/uploads/editor/image/2016-11-22/1479807671949421.png" title="1479807671949421.png" alt="blob.png" style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px auto; outline: none; table-layout: fixed; word-break: break-all; border: none; vertical-align: middle; width: 1124.40625px; height: auto;"/></span></p><p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;与会参加者</p><p style="text-align: center;">听课嘉宾定向邀请</p><p style="text-align: center;">从事摄影、设计、传媒、</p><p style="text-align: center;">文学、艺术、绘画、</p><p style="text-align: center;">音乐、演艺、金融等</p><p style="text-align: center;">不同行业人士</p><p style="text-align: center;">不限年龄性别</p><p style="text-align: center;">为保证现场交流效果</p><p style="text-align: center;">6人为限</p><p style="text-align: center;">以报名先后次序为准</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 22.484375px; outline: none; table-layout: fixed; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 1.4rem; font-weight: 600; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, SimSun, 宋体, sans-serif; text-align: center; white-space: normal;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; outline: none; table-layout: fixed; word-break: break-all;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; outline: none; table-layout: fixed; word-break: break-all; font-size: 16px;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 22.484375px; outline: none; table-layout: fixed; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 1.4rem; font-weight: 600; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, SimSun, 宋体, sans-serif; text-align: center; white-space: normal;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; outline: none; table-layout: fixed; word-break: break-all;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; outline: none; table-layout: fixed; word-break: break-all; font-size: 16px;"><img src="http://zhenghun.yicehua.cn/uploads/editor/image/2016-11-22/1479807722459275.png" title="1479807722459275.png" alt="blob.png" style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px auto; outline: none; table-layout: fixed; word-break: break-all; border: none; vertical-align: middle; width: 1124.40625px; height: auto;"/></span></strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;">课程背景介绍：</p><p style="text-align: center;">冬日，午后，咖啡馆中</p><p style="text-align: center;">一杯温热的伯爵红茶</p><p style="text-align: center;">橙红透明的汤色中荡漾着佛手柑的甜香气韵</p><p style="text-align: center;">尽显英伦文化的时尚</p><p style="text-align: center;">何种爱恨情仇</p><p style="text-align: center;">商场拼杀</p><p style="text-align: center;">都在一缕馨香中袅袅而去</p><p style="text-align: center;">只剩下完整的自己</p><p style="text-align: center;">与心相对</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 22.484375px; outline: none; table-layout: fixed; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 1.4rem; font-weight: 600; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, SimSun, 宋体, sans-serif; text-align: center; white-space: normal;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; outline: none; table-layout: fixed; word-break: break-all; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;"><img src="http://zhenghun.yicehua.cn/uploads/editor/image/2016-11-22/1479808164592672.png" title="1479808164592672.png" alt="blob.png" style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px auto; outline: none; table-layout: fixed; word-break: break-all; border: none; vertical-align: middle; width: 1124.40625px; height: auto;"/></span></p><p style="text-align: center;">这是茶的魅力</p><p style="text-align: center;">都市红尘中不可少的挚友</p><p style="text-align: center;">为什么这种英式红茶的名字叫做伯爵</p><p style="text-align: center;">它独特的口感又是怎样形成、并且传承百年的呢</p><p style="text-align: center;">红茶在传统上是西方知道的唯一的茶</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 22.484375px; outline: none; table-layout: fixed; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 1.4rem; font-weight: 600; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, SimSun, 宋体, sans-serif; text-align: center; white-space: normal;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; outline: none; table-layout: fixed; word-break: break-all; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;"><img src="http://zhenghun.yicehua.cn/uploads/editor/image/2016-11-22/1479808211484465.png" title="1479808211484465.png" alt="blob.png" style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px auto; outline: none; table-layout: fixed; word-break: break-all; border: none; vertical-align: middle; width: 1124.40625px; height: auto;"/><br style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; outline: none; table-layout: fixed; word-break: break-all;"/></span></p><p style="text-align: center;">时空穿越</p><p style="text-align: center;">200年前</p><p style="text-align: center;">传说是因为一次偶然</p><p style="text-align: center;">世界上有了红茶</p><p style="text-align: center;">武夷山桐木关自然保护区的深处</p><p style="text-align: center;">一种带有独特松烟香气的叫作正山小种的红茶</p><p style="text-align: center;">因此成为世界红茶的鼻祖</p><p style="text-align: center;">然而，谁会想到</p><p style="text-align: center;">大山深处的一杯茶</p><p style="text-align: center;">在后来</p><p style="text-align: center;">几乎撼动了整个世界</p><p style="text-align: center;">从1773年的美国独立战争到1840年的鸦片战争</p><p style="text-align: center;">都与它有着直接的关联</p><p style="text-align: center;">从正山小种到格雷伯爵</p><p style="text-align: center;">一场穿越时空的对话</p><p style="text-align: center;">站在红茶的来处坐品红茶</p><p style="text-align: center;">廿四节沏之立冬茶——红茶分享沙龙</p><p style="text-align: center;">与您一起细数伯爵由来、慢品红茶神韵、自在滋味人生</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 22.484375px; outline: none; table-layout: fixed; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 1.4rem; font-weight: 600; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, SimSun, 宋体, sans-serif; text-align: center; white-space: normal;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; outline: none; table-layout: fixed; word-break: break-all;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; outline: none; table-layout: fixed; word-break: break-all; font-size: 16px;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 22.484375px; outline: none; table-layout: fixed; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 1.4rem; font-weight: 600; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, SimSun, 宋体, sans-serif; text-align: center; white-space: normal;"><img src="http://zhenghun.yicehua.cn/uploads/editor/image/2016-11-22/1479807773591910.png" title="1479807773591910.png" alt="blob.png" style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px auto; outline: none; table-layout: fixed; word-break: break-all; border: none; vertical-align: middle; width: 1124.40625px; height: auto;"/></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 22.484375px; outline: none; table-layout: fixed; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 1.4rem; font-weight: 600; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, SimSun, 宋体, sans-serif; text-align: center; white-space: normal; line-height: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; outline: none; table-layout: fixed; word-break: break-all;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; 